Package si.ijs.kt.clus.algo

Class ClusInductionAlgorithm

java.lang.Object
si.ijs.kt.clus.algo.ClusInductionAlgorithm
Direct Known Subclasses:
BestFirstInduce, ClusBeamInduce, ClusBoostingInduce, ClusEnsembleInduce, ClusExhaustiveInduce, ClusRuleConstraintInduce, ClusRuleInduce, ClusSemiSupervisedInduce, DepthFirstInduce, DepthFirstInduceWithOptions, OptXValInduce, ReliefInduce
public abstract class ClusInductionAlgorithm extends Object
Subclasses should implement: public ClusModel induceSingleUnpruned(ClusRun cr); In addition, subclasses may also want to implement (to return more than one model): public void induceAll(ClusRun cr);
